WEBVTT

00:00:00.560 --> 00:00:03.110
Well, good evening, family. Thank you for

00:00:03.120 --> 00:00:05.269
joining us again tonight. We're going to

00:00:05.279 --> 00:00:07.269
pray and sing a little bit.

00:00:07.279 --> 00:00:08.710
I'll sing some songs or whatever the

00:00:08.720 --> 00:00:12.549
Lord has on His heart for me to sing.

00:00:12.559 --> 00:00:15.190
I woke up this morning singing a song

00:00:15.200 --> 00:00:17.269
out of my sleep, so I figured this is

00:00:17.279 --> 00:00:19.670
what He wanted to hear.

00:00:19.680 --> 00:00:22.310
I told Diana, "You know, whenever it

00:00:22.310 --> 00:00:22.320
happens—it

00:00:22.320 --> 00:00:24.710
happens quite often—but this one, I

00:00:24.720 --> 00:00:26.950
haven't heard this song in so long and

00:00:26.960 --> 00:00:29.429
I couldn't believe it. I was

00:00:29.439 --> 00:00:31.830
like, 'Well, that's really

00:00:31.830 --> 00:00:31.840
cool.'"The

00:00:31.840 --> 00:00:34.630
last video

00:00:34.640 --> 00:00:37.590
was heavy, but I really feel in my

00:00:37.600 --> 00:00:41.030
spirit we've made great ground

00:00:41.040 --> 00:00:43.270
concerning praying for our president

00:00:43.280 --> 00:00:45.830
and praying for our nation. I could feel

00:00:45.840 --> 00:00:48.790
the shifting last night as we were

00:00:48.800 --> 00:00:53.110
interceding for our leader,

00:00:53.120 --> 00:00:55.910
and that makes me so happy. It felt so

00:00:55.920 --> 00:00:58.470
good to feel that. For those

00:00:58.470 --> 00:00:58.480
of you

00:00:58.480 --> 00:01:00.389
familiar with what I'm talking

00:01:00.389 --> 00:01:00.399
about—some

00:01:00.399 --> 00:01:02.229
of you are just babies at

00:01:02.239 --> 00:01:05.030
this, but some of you are

00:01:05.030 --> 00:01:05.040
veterans—when

00:01:05.040 --> 00:01:06.870
you get in that river of

00:01:06.880 --> 00:01:10.469
prayer, you can feel the wall or you can

00:01:10.479 --> 00:01:13.109
feel a flow. Sometimes you just keep

00:01:13.119 --> 00:01:15.030
hitting that wall, hitting that

00:01:15.040 --> 00:01:18.630
door until you have it open.

00:01:18.630 --> 00:01:18.640
In

00:01:18.640 --> 00:01:20.469
prayer, a lot of times

00:01:20.469 --> 00:01:20.479
when

00:01:20.479 --> 00:01:23.109
I'm interceding,

00:01:23.119 --> 00:01:24.630
you can feel when other people are

00:01:24.640 --> 00:01:26.469
pulling with you.

00:01:26.479 --> 00:01:29.270
You can feel, in a corporate setting,

00:01:29.280 --> 00:01:30.950
when other people are on the same

00:01:30.960 --> 00:01:34.069
assignment as you in the Spirit. So,

00:01:34.079 --> 00:01:35.749
whenever I'm praying

00:01:35.759 --> 00:01:37.350
over our president and I'm praying over

00:01:37.360 --> 00:01:40.630
this, it's almost

00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:42.069
like

00:01:42.079 --> 00:01:44.310
you're walking through mud, and you're

00:01:44.320 --> 00:01:45.670
pulling and

00:01:45.680 --> 00:01:48.389
trying so hard to gain ground.

00:01:48.399 --> 00:01:49.990
You're grabbing and

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:51.670
clenching and pulling yourself up

00:01:51.680 --> 00:01:54.230
out of it, and then all of a sudden,

00:01:54.240 --> 00:01:57.109
you're on a slide.

00:01:57.119 --> 00:01:59.270
You could

00:01:59.280 --> 00:02:01.510
feel that last night as I was

00:02:01.520 --> 00:02:04.149
interceding. We had times of prayer

00:02:04.159 --> 00:02:06.789
here, and

00:02:06.799 --> 00:02:08.869
I

00:02:08.879 --> 00:02:11.430
want to tell you this:

00:02:11.440 --> 00:02:13.270
faith is not a feeling, and prayer is not

00:02:13.280 --> 00:02:14.710
a feeling. I'm not

00:02:14.720 --> 00:02:16.550
moved by what I see; I'm not moved by

00:02:16.560 --> 00:02:18.309
what I feel. I'm moved by what the

00:02:18.319 --> 00:02:19.910
Word of God says, so don't always go by

00:02:19.920 --> 00:02:21.589
a feeling. But whenever you get

00:02:21.599 --> 00:02:23.190
sensitive to the things of the Spirit,

00:02:23.200 --> 00:02:24.630
you will know what I'm talking about

00:02:24.640 --> 00:02:27.670
more. There is a river, then there's

00:02:27.680 --> 00:02:30.309
dry, and then it's like going

00:02:30.319 --> 00:02:32.309
through mud. You can feel your toil in

00:02:32.319 --> 00:02:33.990
the ground; it's pulling and

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:36.309
pulling. Last night

00:02:36.319 --> 00:02:38.070
you

00:02:38.080 --> 00:02:39.589
could feel that there's so many people

00:02:39.599 --> 00:02:41.110
praying for President Trump and praying

00:02:41.120 --> 00:02:43.670
for this nation. I was excited about

00:02:43.680 --> 00:02:46.150
it. I believe the

00:02:46.160 --> 00:02:48.309
fervent prayer of the righteous availeth

00:02:48.309 --> 00:02:48.319
much—the

00:02:48.319 --> 00:02:51.430
fervent, effectual prayer.

00:02:52.319 --> 00:02:54.229
Honey,

00:02:56.160 --> 00:02:57.589
find the scripture; I don't want to

00:02:57.599 --> 00:03:00.229
misquote it. I

00:03:00.239 --> 00:03:04.070
was looking at Proverbs 15:8:

00:03:04.080 --> 00:03:06.630
"The prayer of the upright is His

00:03:06.630 --> 00:03:06.640
delight."I

00:03:06.640 --> 00:03:10.229
believe tonight, as we

00:03:10.239 --> 00:03:12.630
pray for our president

00:03:12.630 --> 00:03:12.640
and

00:03:12.640 --> 00:03:15.110
our nation, the prayer of the

00:03:15.120 --> 00:03:18.070
upright is His delight. Isn't that

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:19.910
wonderful? I love that;

00:03:19.920 --> 00:03:22.630
He delights in it.

00:03:22.640 --> 00:03:25.589
James 5:16: "The effectual

00:03:25.599 --> 00:03:27.830
fervent prayer of a righteous man

00:03:27.840 --> 00:03:28.869
availeth

00:03:28.879 --> 00:03:30.149
much."The

00:03:30.159 --> 00:03:34.309
fervent, effectual prayer of the

00:03:34.319 --> 00:03:37.589
righteous availeth much.

00:03:37.599 --> 00:03:40.470
We're getting the job done.

00:03:42.159 --> 00:03:44.149
I really believe that's what God has

00:03:44.159 --> 00:03:46.869
called and assigned us to do

00:03:46.879 --> 00:03:52.070
for such a time as this.

00:03:56.080 --> 00:03:57.750
The effectual fervent prayer of a

00:03:57.760 --> 00:03:59.830
righteous man availeth much.

00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:02.869
And that's who we are.

00:04:02.879 --> 00:04:04.710
Braden's grinning at

00:04:04.710 --> 00:04:04.720
me;

00:04:04.720 --> 00:04:08.949
I get

00:04:08.949 --> 00:04:08.959
tongue-tied.

00:04:08.959 --> 00:04:11.910
All glory to Jesus. Isn't that

00:04:11.920 --> 00:04:13.750
wonderful? I believe that's what

00:04:13.760 --> 00:04:16.390
we're doing and we'll continue to do

00:04:16.400 --> 00:04:19.430
all throughout 2026 and the rest of

00:04:19.440 --> 00:04:22.310
this year, praying over what I believe

00:04:22.320 --> 00:04:27.189
the Lord has shown us through prayer.

00:04:27.189 --> 00:04:27.199
We're

00:04:27.199 --> 00:04:31.430
praying over these major events

00:04:31.430 --> 00:04:31.440
where

00:04:31.440 --> 00:04:33.749
I believe we have power and

00:04:33.759 --> 00:04:37.189
authority. As we prayed into the storm

00:04:37.199 --> 00:04:39.430
and took authority over it,

00:04:39.440 --> 00:04:41.510
there wasn't as much damage as they

00:04:41.520 --> 00:04:43.670
were thinking. We didn't have as much

00:04:43.680 --> 00:04:48.469
snow as we were expecting.

00:04:48.469 --> 00:04:48.479
Maybe

00:04:48.479 --> 00:04:51.110
some people got a lot,

00:04:52.800 --> 00:04:55.510
but our area, when we got out today,

00:04:55.520 --> 00:04:57.670
didn't seem

00:04:59.840 --> 00:05:02.390
way bad. Based on what we

00:05:02.400 --> 00:05:04.310
could see on the news, it

00:05:04.320 --> 00:05:06.150
could have been a lot worse, with

00:05:06.150 --> 00:05:06.160
many

00:05:06.160 --> 00:05:07.510
more power

00:05:07.520 --> 00:05:10.150
outages.

00:05:10.160 --> 00:05:12.550
I believe it's because the people were praying. As

00:05:12.560 --> 00:05:15.430
big as that storm was and as big as

00:05:15.440 --> 00:05:18.150
that event could have been, it

00:05:18.160 --> 00:05:20.230
could have been more catastrophic.

00:05:20.240 --> 00:05:23.670
So, we give all the glory to Jesus today.

00:05:23.680 --> 00:05:25.749
If you're without

00:05:25.759 --> 00:05:28.710
power, it's terrible, but I

00:05:28.720 --> 00:05:30.469
believe they'll get it on quickly. Let's

00:05:30.479 --> 00:05:31.749
pray that they get it on quickly

00:05:31.759 --> 00:05:33.590
tonight, that they'll have all the power

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:35.909
up, and that you won't be without your electricity

00:05:35.909 --> 00:05:35.919
and

00:05:35.919 --> 00:05:37.430
heat.

00:05:37.440 --> 00:05:39.430
They'll be able to do a

00:05:39.440 --> 00:05:41.350
quick work and get to you

00:05:41.350 --> 00:05:41.360
fast.

00:05:41.360 --> 00:05:43.909
You'll have favor where

00:05:43.909 --> 00:05:43.919
everyone

00:05:43.919 --> 00:05:45.430
else doesn't. You'll

00:05:45.440 --> 00:05:46.870
have favor because you're a child of the

00:05:46.880 --> 00:05:49.270
King. I believe that God's favored you

00:05:49.280 --> 00:05:51.430
today and put

00:05:51.440 --> 00:05:53.189
goodness and mercy on you, and it's following

00:05:53.199 --> 00:05:55.749
you all the days of your life. I stand

00:05:55.759 --> 00:05:58.390
on that and we believe it. We're

00:05:58.400 --> 00:06:01.430
believing believers who are receivers,

00:06:01.440 --> 00:06:04.070
and we're contenders for the glory.

00:06:04.080 --> 00:06:06.790
We're contenders for the

00:06:06.790 --> 00:06:06.800
end-time

00:06:06.800 --> 00:06:09.110
anointing, the

00:06:09.120 --> 00:06:11.909
outpouring of finances,

00:06:11.909 --> 00:06:11.919
and

00:06:11.919 --> 00:06:13.990
whatever God has for us. We will

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:17.590
lack no good thing. I believe that,

00:06:17.600 --> 00:06:19.430
so that's what we're going to stand on

00:06:19.440 --> 00:06:21.749
tonight. We see the things in the

00:06:21.759 --> 00:06:24.309
news from Carney, the Prime

00:06:24.319 --> 00:06:26.950
Minister of Canada.

00:06:29.919 --> 00:06:31.350
I thought it was interesting because of

00:06:31.360 --> 00:06:33.189
the prophetic words the Lord has given

00:06:33.199 --> 00:06:35.510
us and the visions we've seen about him

00:06:35.520 --> 00:06:39.670
going to China and saying, "Hey, I want

00:06:39.680 --> 00:06:42.230
to do business with you."This was

00:06:42.240 --> 00:06:46.230
his last major push, from what I saw in the

00:06:46.240 --> 00:06:51.510
Spirit, for his country to

00:06:51.520 --> 00:06:54.309
pull itself out of this hole. I

00:06:54.309 --> 00:06:54.319
saw

00:06:54.319 --> 00:06:57.189
Canada going into

00:06:57.199 --> 00:06:59.589
a depression and joining up with

00:06:59.599 --> 00:07:02.870
America in the days

00:07:02.870 --> 00:07:02.880
ahead—not

00:07:02.880 --> 00:07:05.830
saying Canada is dissolved, like I keep

00:07:05.840 --> 00:07:07.749
hearing President Trump saying '51st

00:07:07.749 --> 00:07:07.759
state'and

00:07:07.759 --> 00:07:10.150
all this, but a financial

00:07:10.150 --> 00:07:10.160
merger.

00:07:10.160 --> 00:07:12.950
Their currency

00:07:12.960 --> 00:07:15.830
became our currency; that's what I saw. We

00:07:15.840 --> 00:07:19.430
still had borders, but

00:07:19.430 --> 00:07:19.440
their

00:07:19.440 --> 00:07:22.629
currency and Mexico's

00:07:22.639 --> 00:07:25.830
currency became one.

00:07:25.840 --> 00:07:27.350
This is what I've been praying over

00:07:27.360 --> 00:07:29.589
for two years. I

00:07:29.589 --> 00:07:29.599
think

00:07:29.599 --> 00:07:31.589
some things the Lord shows us

00:07:31.589 --> 00:07:31.599
happen

00:07:31.599 --> 00:07:33.589
really quickly, like

00:07:33.599 --> 00:07:35.670
the storm coming. We saw that back on

00:07:35.680 --> 00:07:37.670
November 11th, and we've been

00:07:37.680 --> 00:07:39.350
praying over it. We saw it on October

00:07:39.360 --> 00:07:42.710
29th, and then we saw it again—was

00:07:42.710 --> 00:07:42.720
it in

00:07:42.720 --> 00:07:45.749
July?

00:07:45.759 --> 00:07:47.510
He's been talking to us about this

00:07:47.520 --> 00:07:49.510
for seven months.

00:07:49.520 --> 00:07:50.950
He talked about October and

00:07:50.960 --> 00:07:51.909
November, too.

00:07:51.919 --> 00:07:54.390
So, we've had these cues to

00:07:54.390 --> 00:07:54.400
pray

00:07:54.400 --> 00:07:57.029
over the weather and this storm.

00:07:57.039 --> 00:07:59.350
I believe we prayed

00:07:59.360 --> 00:08:01.990
over it and saw results. When

00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:05.510
we see Canada and Mexico joining

00:08:05.520 --> 00:08:07.909
up with the United States to

00:08:07.919 --> 00:08:10.629
have a currency, it's when I saw

00:08:10.639 --> 00:08:13.510
them trying to come against the

00:08:13.520 --> 00:08:15.430
dollar and the BRICS in the days ahead

00:08:15.440 --> 00:08:17.909
to bring a stronger

00:08:17.919 --> 00:08:21.909
currency system.

00:08:24.639 --> 00:08:26.869
We keep praying into that.

00:08:26.879 --> 00:08:29.189
All I know is it's all leading up to

00:08:29.199 --> 00:08:31.909
the Mark of the Beast and

00:08:31.909 --> 00:08:31.919
the

00:08:31.919 --> 00:08:34.709
One World Order. What will

00:08:40.880 --> 00:08:44.389
be the lynchpin for the One World

00:08:44.399 --> 00:08:47.590
Order and the one-world currency?

00:08:47.600 --> 00:08:50.790
I believe truly—and this is just

00:08:50.790 --> 00:08:50.800
Braden

00:08:50.800 --> 00:08:52.310
and me thinking, I can't speak

00:08:52.320 --> 00:08:53.750
for Diana, though I know she agrees

00:08:53.760 --> 00:08:55.509
with

00:08:55.519 --> 00:08:59.350
everything—the

00:08:59.360 --> 00:09:02.070
Rapture of the Church

00:09:02.080 --> 00:09:04.389
could be the

00:09:04.389 --> 00:09:04.399
lynchpin.

00:09:04.399 --> 00:09:06.150
The

00:09:06.160 --> 00:09:09.190
total meltdown of society will happen when

00:09:11.279 --> 00:09:13.509
hundreds of millions, if not a billion,

00:09:13.509 --> 00:09:13.519
believers are

00:09:13.519 --> 00:09:16.389
taken out of here

00:09:16.389 --> 00:09:16.399
in

00:09:16.399 --> 00:09:18.949
the Rapture of the Church. Now, there

00:09:18.949 --> 00:09:18.959
are

00:09:18.959 --> 00:09:20.150
a lot of people who don't believe that, but

00:09:20.160 --> 00:09:21.910
I'm trying to say: what is the

00:09:21.910 --> 00:09:21.920
lynchpin

00:09:21.920 --> 00:09:24.630
that pushes this over?

00:09:24.640 --> 00:09:27.110
War, rumors of war, plague. The plague

00:09:27.120 --> 00:09:30.710
that I've seen coming in 2020, 2028,

00:09:30.720 --> 00:09:34.070
the spring and fall of 2027,

00:09:34.080 --> 00:09:36.389
going into 2028, is when I've seen a

00:09:36.399 --> 00:09:38.790
great shaking coming. Now, some

00:09:38.800 --> 00:09:41.110
people say that's too early, Brandon. I

00:09:41.120 --> 00:09:42.790
believe that it's further down the road.

00:09:42.800 --> 00:09:44.630
I believe we're going to see an economic

00:09:44.640 --> 00:09:46.310
crisis

00:09:46.320 --> 00:09:49.990
before we see the plague.

00:09:52.399 --> 00:09:55.430
This is what I saw when I was praying:

00:09:57.680 --> 00:10:01.590
the financial

00:10:01.590 --> 00:10:01.600
and

00:10:01.600 --> 00:10:04.470
economic situation and the

00:10:04.480 --> 00:10:06.070
plague go hand in hand. They ride

00:10:06.080 --> 00:10:07.670
together.

00:10:07.680 --> 00:10:09.750
They're like twins.

00:10:09.760 --> 00:10:14.710
Famine and plague ride together.

00:10:14.720 --> 00:10:17.190
And so,

00:10:17.200 --> 00:10:18.870
you know, that's just me looking

00:10:18.880 --> 00:10:20.389
into it. I don't want to add to or

00:10:20.399 --> 00:10:22.310
take away from anything. It's just me

00:10:22.320 --> 00:10:23.590
trying to figure it out with my natural

00:10:23.600 --> 00:10:25.269
mind and say, "Listen, Lord, how close

00:10:25.279 --> 00:10:27.670
are you to your coming? How close are we?"There

00:10:27.670 --> 00:10:27.680
are

00:10:27.680 --> 00:10:29.910
a lot of people

00:10:29.910 --> 00:10:29.920
who

00:10:29.920 --> 00:10:31.670
believe He could come back in the next

00:10:31.680 --> 00:10:33.750
five minutes. I believe no man knows

00:10:33.760 --> 00:10:34.710
the day or the hour; that's what the

00:10:34.720 --> 00:10:36.550
Bible says. But we can see the signs of

00:10:36.560 --> 00:10:39.030
the times looking all around us.

00:10:39.040 --> 00:10:42.710
We see Iran

00:10:42.720 --> 00:10:45.590
and all the uprisings and the regime

00:10:45.600 --> 00:10:47.590
change that I believe is about to

00:10:47.600 --> 00:10:53.269
happen in Cuba, Mexico, and

00:10:53.269 --> 00:10:53.279
so

00:10:53.279 --> 00:10:57.030
on, as part of this

00:10:57.030 --> 00:10:57.040
end-time

00:10:57.040 --> 00:11:00.150
move. Here we see some

00:11:00.160 --> 00:11:02.150
people are saying, "Is this the ten kings

00:11:02.160 --> 00:11:06.550
rising up in Gaza with the

00:11:06.560 --> 00:11:09.910
president and Jared Kushner

00:11:09.920 --> 00:11:14.069
running this, and the new

00:11:14.079 --> 00:11:17.110
Gaza Strip and all the beauty of the

00:11:17.120 --> 00:11:18.790
buildings that they're

00:11:18.790 --> 00:11:18.800
promising?"And

00:11:18.800 --> 00:11:20.790
they have oil derricks, and they put that

00:11:20.800 --> 00:11:23.269
off to the side, a little bit over here.

00:11:23.279 --> 00:11:24.949
I thought that was interesting. The

00:11:24.959 --> 00:11:26.710
beautiful landscape I told you

00:11:26.720 --> 00:11:29.269
looked like Miami; that's what I saw in

00:11:29.279 --> 00:11:31.269
the spirit. And the Lord said, "But I

00:11:31.279 --> 00:11:34.230
saw oil, oil, oil and gas, gas,

00:11:34.230 --> 00:11:34.240
gas."I

00:11:34.240 --> 00:11:36.949
said there was so much money, billions

00:11:36.959 --> 00:11:39.030
of dollars in the

00:11:39.040 --> 00:11:41.670
Mediterranean, outside of Gaza.

00:11:41.680 --> 00:11:44.470
I saw so much money down in there. It

00:11:44.480 --> 00:11:46.790
was a pocket of oil that was one of the

00:11:46.800 --> 00:11:51.430
largest reserves in the world.

00:11:51.440 --> 00:11:52.949
And the Lord said, "I put that there

